data.description: Spacious brick ranch with a large fenced front, and back yard! 3 Bedrooms, 2 Full baths with lots to offer. Open concept dining room, living room area. The back yard, and rear patio is perfect for entertaining. The patio has a pool side platform that is perfect for relaxing by the pool when the weather warms up. Part of yard has been seeded, and old inground pool in back corner was filled in recently. Attached T.V's & Mounts, window units, and electric fireplace will not convey. Duct work needs to be installed for central HVAC unit. Above ground pool was just closed for the season. S. GASTONIA FD tax district.
